## Bulk search by attribute

```shell
curl -i -X POST -H "Content-Type: application/json" --data-binary "@data.json" https://<%= config[:api_endpoint] %>/crm/search/bulk

# data.json
{
  "shop_id": "1234567890",
  "shop_secret": "0987654321",
  "by": "loyalty_id",
  "ids": ["L01", "L02"]
}
```

